="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/water_culture.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-87"><img class="size-medium wp-image-87 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/water_culture-300x188.jpg" alt="water_culture" width="300" height="188" /></a>\r\n<span class="apple-converted-space"><strong>¬†H·ªá th·ªëng ng·∫≠p &amp; r√∫t ƒë·ªãnh k·ª≥ (ebb v√† flow system):</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">¬†kh√¥ng gi·ªëng nh∆∞ h·ªá th·ªëng th·ªßy canh ·ªü tr√™n, ph·∫ßn r·ªÖ c√¢y lu√¥n ch√¨m trong n∆∞·ªõc ch·ªâ th√≠ch h·ª£p cho 1 s·ªë √≠t c√¢y tr·ªìng. H·ªá th·ªëng ng·∫≠p v√† r√∫t ƒë·ªãnh k·ª≥ c√≥ m·ªôt m√°y b∆°m ƒëi·ªÅu khi·ªÉn ƒë·ªÉ c√≥ th·ªÉ b∆°m dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng v√†o khay tr·ªìng v√† r√∫t ra theo chu k·ª≥ ƒë√£ ƒë∆∞·ª£c ƒë·ªãnh s·∫µn. Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y r·ªÖ c√¢y s·∫Ω c√≥ nh·ªØng l√∫c kh√¥ng ng·∫≠p trong n∆∞·ªõc ƒë·ªÉ ‚Äúth·ªü‚Äù m·ªôt c√°ch t·ª± nhi√™n, tr√°nh b·ªã ng·ªôp. H·ªá th·ªëng n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ d√πng ƒë·ªÉ tr·ªìng c√† chua, khoai t√¢y.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/ebb_and_flow.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-86"><img class="size-medium wp-image-86 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/ebb_and_flow-300x188.jpg" alt="ebb_and_flow" width="300" height="188" /></a>\r\n<strong>H·ªá th·ªëng nh·ªè gi·ªçt (Drip systems):</strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><strong>¬†</strong>h·ªá th·ªëng nh·ªè gi·ªçt l√† lo·∫°i h·ªá th·ªëng hydroponics ƒë∆∞·ª£c s·ª≠ d·ª•ng r·ªông r√£i nh·∫•t tr√™n th·∫ø gi·ªõi. M√°y b∆°m s·∫Ω b∆°m dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng l√™n, nh·ªè tr·ª±c ti·∫øp v√†o g·ªëc c·ªßa c√¢y tr·ªìng b·ªüi nh·ªØng ƒë∆∞·ªùng ·ªëng nh·ªè gi·ªçt theo ƒë·ªãnh k·ª≥. Dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng d∆∞ ch·∫£y xu·ªëng s·∫Ω ƒë∆∞·ª£c thu h·ªìi trong b·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng. Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y, h·ªá th·ªëng n√†y s·ª≠ d·ª•ng dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng kh√° hi·ªáu qu·∫£, n∆∞·ªõc d∆∞ ra ƒë∆∞·ª£c t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng, kh√¥ng b·ªã hao ph√≠. H·ªá th·ªëng n√†y c√≥ th·ªÉ d√πng ƒë·ªÉ tr·ªìng c√¢y th·∫£o m·ªôc v√† c√°c lo·∫°i hoa.</span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/drip_system.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-85"><img class="size-medium wp-image-85 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/drip_system-300x188.jpg" alt="drip_system" width="300" height="188" /></a>\r\n<span class="apple-converted-space"><strong>¬†H·ªá th·ªëng ‚Äúm√†ng dinh d∆∞·ª°ng‚Äù NFT (Nutrient Film Technique):</strong><span class="apple-converted-space">¬†trong h·ªá th·ªëng m√†ng dinh d∆∞·ª°ng, dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng ƒë∆∞·ª£c b∆°m li√™n t·ª•c v√†o khay tr·ªìng v√† ch·∫£y qua r·ªÖ c·ªßa c√¢y, sau ƒë√≥ ch√∫ng ch·∫£y v·ªÅ b·ªìn ch·ª©a ƒë·ªÉ t√°i s·ª≠ d·ª•ng. Th∆∞·ªùng th√¨ trong h·ªá th·ªëng m√†ng dinh d∆∞·ª°ng kh√¥ng c·∫ßn d√πng th√™m ch·∫•t tr·ªìng, gi√∫p ti·∫øt ki·ªám chi ph√≠ thay ch·∫•t tr·ªìng sau m·ªói v·ª• m√πa. H·ªá th·ªëng n√†y th∆∞·ªùng s·ª≠ d·ª•ng trong quy m√¥ l·ªõn v·ªõi m·ª•c ƒë√≠ch th∆∞∆°ng m·∫°i.</span></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/nft.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-84"><img class="size-medium wp-image-84 aligncenter" src="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/nft-300x188.jpg" alt="nft" width="300" height="188" /></a>\r\n<strong>¬†Kh√≠ canh (Aeroponics):</strong><span class="apple-converted-space"><strong>¬†</strong>l√† h·ªá th·ªëng hydroponics d·∫°ng k·ªπ thu·∫≠t cao nh·∫•t. Gi·ªëng nh∆∞ h·ªá th·ªëng m√†ng dinh d∆∞·ª°ng, ch·∫•t tr·ªìng ch·ªß y·∫øu l√† kh√¥ng kh√≠. R·ªÖ ph∆°i trong kh√¥ng kh√≠ v√† ƒë∆∞·ª£c phun s∆∞∆°ng b·∫±ng dung d·ªãch dinh d∆∞·ª°ng. Vi·ªác phun s∆∞∆°ng th∆∞·ªùng ƒë∆∞·ª£c th·ª±c hi·ªán m·ªói v√†i ph√∫t. Nh∆∞ v·∫≠y, c√¢y v·ª´a c√≥ ƒë·ªß th·ª©c ƒÉn, v·ª´a c√≥ ƒë·ªß n∆∞·ªõc u·ªëng v√† lu√¥n c√≥ kh√¥ng kh√≠ ƒë·ªÉ th·ªü.<span class="apple-converted-space">¬†</span></span>\r\n\r\n<a href="http://localhost/gwall/wp-content/uploads/2016/02/aeroponics.jpg" rel="attachment wp-att-83"><img class="size-medium wp-image-83 aligncenter" src="http://localhos